v 3
d splink: Probabilistic record linkage using the Fellegi-Sunter model
d
d Full-fidelity implementation matching the Python splink package.
d Features: configurable comparison levels, multiple comparison functions
d (JW, Jaro, Levenshtein, DL, Jaccard, exact, numeric), multiple blocking
d rules with OR logic, term frequency adjustments, null handling, pairwise
d output, and cross-dataset linking.
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260223
